storageTypes.Counter/Shelf: Room temperature, kitchen counter or shelf

metadata.notes: Shelf life assumes proper storage. Times are guidelines and vary by item quality and home conditions. Items marked 'Not applicable/needed' for frozen cannot be frozen or don't benefit from freezing.
